              <tr><td><strong>Diversification</strong></td><td>Content outside usual interests</td><td>Discovery of new niches by the user</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 id="examples">Real FYP examples</h2>
        <p>Three small-business videos that hit the FYP and why.</p>

        <h3>1. Memphis sourdough bakery</h3>
        <div class="url-flow">
