        <p>theStacc plans and publishes short-form video content across TikTok, Reels, and Shorts on autopilot. Our engine surfaces the topics your audience is actually searching for, generates scripts and captions optimised for completion, then schedules and publishes at your peak activity window. The result: FYP reach without a full-time social team.</p>

